data.description: This beautiful maintained 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms home is close proximity to near by shopping centers, restaurants, hospitals and boat landings. Perfectly located in the heart of Moncks Corner in the desirable subdivision  First St. Johns! Inside you will find a traditional  open floor plan with a living room/dining room combo freshly painted that flows into the kitchen boasting a uniquely fully upgraded kitchen with TONS OF UPGRADES, a considerably amount of cabinet space and a pantry. Entering the home, to your right  there will be a bonus area that can be used for an additional family room, playroom , or whatever suits your style. Both bathrooms are updated, there's a covered patio and fence backyard!!
